description: COOKEVILLE, Tenn. â€“ Another grueling day at the ballpark saw the Tennessee Tech baseball team bounce back and even its Ohio Valley Conference series with in-state rival Austin Peay Saturday afternoon, as the Golden Eagles (24-23, 8-12) took down the Governors (19-32, 10-10) by a final score of 10-7.
